net.objectzoo.events.Event4

Packages that use Event4
net.objectzoo.events.impl This package contains support classes that implement EventDelegates ready to be used. 
 

Uses of Event4 in net.objectzoo.events.impl
 

Subinterfaces of Event4 in net.objectzoo.events.impl
 interface Event4AsyncDelegate<T1,T2,T3,T4>
          An Event4AsyncDelegate implements Action4Async as well as Event4Delegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action4Async interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the Event4Delegate interface.
 interface Event4Delegate<T1,T2,T3,T4>
          An Event4Delegate implements Action4 as well as Event4 and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the Action4 interface to all subscribers of the Event4 interface.
 

Classes in net.objectzoo.events.impl that implement Event4
 class Event4AsyncAdapter<T1,T2,T3,T4>
          The Event4AsyncAdapter is class that adapts an Event4Delegate to Event4AsyncDelegate so that the original delegates subscribers can be invoked asynchronously.
 class Event4Caller<T1,T2,T3,T4>
          The Event4Caller is a Event4Delegate implementation that allows event distribution to a single subscriber.
 class Event4Distributor<T1,T2,T3,T4>
          The Event4Distributor is a Event4Delegate implementation that allows event distribution to multiple subscribers.
